{"tid":1897121,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 80 & 90後 登陸方舟最後召集","createTime":"2020-02-25T13:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T19:50:55.000Z","uid":55129,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15f7105527745809975495ecc0a1ccb6a87a4e02","tid":1897121,"uid":55129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"我地係限載 80 90後諾亞方舟<br />\n歡迎咁多位巴絲打捉緊機會上船<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認識下港九新界既新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘有個係你左近<br />\n仲有好多活動(即興飯局/唱K/行山/etc)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要你肯出聚(唔係硬性)就可以申請啦<br />\n鐘意鳩噏/識朋友/出聚飲嘢快啲入黎一齊玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係屋企home office到悶悶地/無所事事嘅你唔入黎等幾時<br />\n填完下面張form好快就會有人搵你架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/hoKgFqY985Jvoemx5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhoKgFqY985Jvoemx5&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=7697c23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hoKgFqY985Jvoemx5</a><br />\n<br />\n潛水/狗公/娘娘/藍即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c34c0bcbb631872ae44aadb14185a390b28f1b","tid":1897121,"uid":243290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我小雞雞幫你推下"},{"pid":"8a5b5580df28b896784f4886cee8194ff124bc69","tid":1897121,"uid":55129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aefaf38f7dddf61eb13323ece5b2e80cb846c705","tid":1897121,"uid":243290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a5b5580df28b896784f4886cee8194ff124bc69","tid":1897121,"uid":55129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"rep